How to make a logo for your brand

Create Your Logo

To design your logo,
follow these 5 simple steps:

1. Tell us about your brand

Fill in the name of your brand or business, plus a tagline if you have one, to our logo maker.

2. Share your design style

Choose from different style options so we can create a custom logo to fit your brand.

3. Customize your logo design

Pick a logo design and customize its fonts, colors, icons and more to make it your own.

4. Download your logo

Get high-quality image files and use your custom logo design anywhere you need to.

5. Print your logo

Create and print business cards and branded merchandise like mugs, t-shirts and tote bags.

Tips for creating a professional logo design

Personality

Establish your brand personality. Imagine it as a person—what characteristics and attributes would it have?

Colors

The right palette can be a powerful tool to create good logos and influence people’s perception of your brand.

Audience

Determine who your target audience is. Take a look at competitors to gain some perspective and inspiration.

Styles

Pick the right style to reflect your brand’s vibe, from modern, to minimalist or retro and anything in between.

FAQ

What is the Wix Logo Maker?

The Wix Logo Maker is an online design tool powered by Artificial Intelligence (AI) that allows you to create and customize a professional logo for free.

How can I create a logo design for my business?

Answer a few simple questions about your brand identity and personal style and the Wix Logo Maker will create a unique logo that fits all your needs—whether its a company logo or a personal logo, you’ll be able to create the perfect one for you.

What files do I get with my purchased logo?

With our logo editor, you get all the types of files that you need for your business, unlike with other logo software platforms. With the Wix Logo Maker you'll receive different logo formats depending on the package you choose. All of the packages include the high-resolution PNG files (5000 x 5000 px) in your original logo colors as well as black, white, and transparent color variations. These files are ideal for using online. If you're planning on printing your logo from the logo creator, we recommend purchasing one of the packages that include high quality SVG vector files.

Can I create a logo for free?

You can create your own logo for free with the Wix Logo Maker. If you need high-resolution files, you can purchase and download your logo from the logo maker at any time.

Do I own my logo after downloading it?

You get full commercial usage rights to your logo after choosing a package that allows you to buy and download it. You’ll be able to use your royalty-free logo wherever and whenever you like.

Can I edit my logo after purchasing/downloading it?

In short, yes, you can, though it depends on your plan. With some of our plans, you have the option to edit your logo after downloading it. For unlimited customization, we recommend choosing the 'Brand Plus' plan (logo-only) or the 'Business' and 'Unlimited' plans (logo + online presence). These plans give you the freedom to make updates to your logo’s design even after downloading the logo files.
